│ 1013 /// disambiguate memory accesses, or they may want the  │
│ nearest dominating                                           │
│ 1014 /// may-aliasing MemoryDef for a call or a store. This  │
│ API enables a                                                │
│ 1015 /// standardized interface to getting and using that    │
