│ for determining the defining memory access for a cloned      │
│ memory access. It handles both `MemoryDef` and `MemoryPhi`   │
│ nodes, ensuring that the cloned memory access is correctly   │
│ linked to its defining access. If the defining access is not │
│ directly cloned, it recursively looks up the defining access │
│ for the original memory access.                              │
